to "other".  In pickos at line 207-208 there is a duplicated line for SunOS:
           /Mozilla.*\(.*;.*; SunOS.*\)/   && do {return "SunOS";};
           /Mozilla.*\(.*;.*; SunOS.*\)/   && do {return "SunOS";};
